text: Seyed Hossein Moareb (born 23 August 1947) is an Iranian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 63 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Iranian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Iran Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Mashhad
